            <p><g>+</g> Ἀναπ<supplied reason="undefined">άη</supplied>
               <lb/> ὁ μακάριος Σε<unclear>ρ</unclear><lb break="no"/>γίος ἐν μηνὶ <unclear>Δί</unclear><lb break="no"/>ου <num>ιϛʹ</num> <expan><abbr>ἰνδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></expan>
